overview: The user initiated a request to significantly enhance the aesthetic
  appeal of their sleep questionnaire application, which they felt was too
  generic. The approach involved a comprehensive review of existing styles,
  followed by a strategic overhaul. Key decisions included adopting a calming,
  sleep-themed color palette with deep indigos, purples, and teals, and
  introducing subtle visual enhancements like background blurs and patterned
  overlays. All core UI components such as checkboxes, radio buttons, sliders,
  and progress bars were redesigned for a more polished look. The main
  questionnaire form, intro section, and report section received significant
  layout and styling improvements. Crucially, the new card-style section
  groupings were consistently applied across all questionnaire sections,
  replacing the previous plain gray boxes. The outcome is a visually cohesive,
  professional, and inviting application that aligns well with a sleep health
  assessment experience.
